      <title>斯塔维利出售后纽卡斯尔联队价值飙升至 10 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/newcastle-united-s-value-soars-to-1-billion-after-staveley-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，沙特老板收购了纽卡斯尔联队前老板阿曼达·斯塔维利 (Amanda Staveley) 的股份，增加了持股量，目前该队的估值超过 10 亿英镑（13 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/newcastle-united-s-value-soars-to-1-billion-after-staveley-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:42:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
